fill

TI (x) 186 -179 placeBL
(y) 0 -10 placeBR
(z ) 50 -155 placeTR
SYM (= 60) show
(40) 81 -155 placeTC
(20) 100 -155 placeTC
(0) 119 -155 placeTC
(-20) 137 -155 placeTC
